reviews.review_text: charlie miller help charlie i love all your work please post a sbd of this smokin show

Oh, Babe...... Never heard this one done electric in all my years of listening.  ......it is a beauty to hear Brent tinklin' along on this acoustic classic.  Great show, not too bad of aud quality, but a crispy SBD would be a real treat.
